\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{2}(v)=\sum g_{j}(v^{(j)}),\quad v^{(j)}\in\mathbb{R}^{p_{j}}
\]

\end_inset

and 
\begin_inset Formula $v=[(v^{(1)})^{T},\dots,(v^{(J)})^{T}]^{T}$
\end_inset

.
